FBIS3-11452 "drlat055_k_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-055 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Mar 1994 SOUTH AMERICA Argentina Socialists, Workers `Repudiate' Gore's Presence PY2103172394 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS in Spanish 1607 GMT 21 Mar 94 PY2103172394 Buenos Aires NOTICIAS ARGENTINAS Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Buenos Aires,21 Mar (NA) -- Members of the Socialist Workers Movement (MST) and the Workers Party (PO) are waiting at the entrance of the Sheraton Hotel to "repudiate the presence in the country" of U.S. Vice President Albert Gore. Gore arrived in Argentina last night and is now attending the opening ceremony of the World Telecommunications Conference at the Libertador Hall of the Sheraton Hotel in Buenos Aires.
